{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01Ht2oeFcxYMyQ97gU7CLz1r","type":"tool_result","content":"  2480→## 6. Key Takeaways\n  2481→\n  2482→1. **Stop ralph.** This is no longer an action item — it is a prerequisite for any further productive work. Every minute ralph runs, it will corrupt state again.\n  2483→\n  2484→2. **Fix the reconciliation guard before any other work.** The next session must apply `if (current === 'done') return` in the reconciliation path. Not document it. Not discuss it. Apply it.\n  2485→\n  2486→3. **Ten identical retrospectives is a system design failure.** The retro process assumes humans read action items and act on them between sessions. When sessions are autonomous and back-to-back, action items from one retro are never read before the next session starts. The process model is broken for autonomous execution.\n  2487→\n  2488→4. **Cost monitoring needs automated thresholds.** When a session completes zero stories and only fixes state, the system should refuse to start the next session without human approval.\n  2489→\n  2490→## 7. Action Items\n  2491→\n  2492→| # | Action | Priority | Owner | Status |\n  2493→|---|--------|----------|-------|--------|\n  2494→| 1 | **Fix state reconciliation to treat `done` as terminal** — add guard: `if (current === 'done') return` in reconciliation path. | CRITICAL | Infrastructure | OPEN — **unfixed for 10 consecutive sessions. One-line fix. Now a $20+ waste item.** |\n  2495→| 2 | **Stop ralph immediately** — the sprint is complete, ralph is burning tokens in an infinite loop. | CRITICAL | User | OPEN — **carried from session 16. Still running. 10 wasted sessions.** |\n  2496→| 3 | **Add ralph sprint-complete termination** — refuse to launch sessions when `sprint.done === sprint.total`. | CRITICAL | Infrastructure | OPEN — **unfixed since session 9** |\n  2497→| 4 | **Make reconciliation proof-document-aware** — check git for proof docs before modifying story status. | HIGH | Infrastructure | OPEN — carried from session 13 |\n  2498→| 5 | **Add circuit breaker for repeated identical fixes** — detect N identical state corruptions and halt. | HIGH | Infrastructure | OPEN — carried from session 15 |\n  2499→| 6 | **Convert retro action items to stories** — action items that survive 10+ retros are a process failure. Create sprint 2 stories from items 1, 3-5. | HIGH | Process | OPEN — carried from session 13 |\n  2500→| 7 | **Reduce \"unknown\" story cost bucket** — $128.04 (20.0%) unattributed cost, growing each no-op session. | LOW | Tooling | OPEN — carried forward |\n  2501→| 8 | **Plan next sprint** — all 16 epics complete. Action items 1, 3-6 above must be the first stories. | HIGH | PM | OPEN — carried forward |\n  2502→"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_01FuRY7MubihCm9AuNVcYqKC","session_id":"94a00213-6144-4c24-a440-4acde8467da0","uuid":"855764f7-780a-4af0-9e86-183c9ea500d7","timestamp":"2026-03-27T14:52:04.659Z"}
