{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01QBGNazDZY6kMPTqCwntUL5","type":"tool_result","content":"     1→# Harness Cost Report\n     2→\n     3→Total API-equivalent cost: $643.38\n     4→Total API calls: 4766\n     5→Average cost per story: $3.36 (153 stories)\n     6→\n     7→## Cost by Token Type\n     8→\n     9→| Type | Tokens | Rate | Cost | % |\n    10→|------|--------|------|------|---|\n    11→| Cache reads | 263,717,996 | $1.50/MTok | $395.58 | 61% |\n    12→| Cache writes | 7,904,184 | $18.75/MTok | $148.20 | 23% |\n    13→| Output | 1,325,645 | $75/MTok | $99.42 | 15% |\n    14→| Input | 11,600 | $15/MTok | $0.17 | 0% |\n    15→\n    16→## Cost by Phase\n    17→\n    18→| Phase | Calls | Cost | % |\n    19→|-------|-------|------|---|\n    20→| verify | 2853 | $359.50 | 55.9% |\n    21→| orchestrator | 544 | $119.21 | 18.5% |\n    22→| retro | 449 | $63.31 | 9.8% |\n    23→| create-story | 344 | $36.58 | 5.7% |\n    24→| code-review | 305 | $34.70 | 5.4% |\n    25→| dev-story | 271 | $30.07 | 4.7% |\n    26→\n    27→## Cost by Tool\n    28→\n    29→| Tool | Calls | Cost | % |\n    30→|------|-------|------|---|\n    31→| Bash | 2022 | $248.53 | 38.6% |\n    32→| Read | 923 | $122.42 | 19.0% |\n    33→| Edit | 616 | $78.93 | 12.3% |\n    34→| Agent | 430 | $56.62 | 8.8% |\n    35→| Skill | 130 | $47.57 | 7.4% |\n    36→| Grep | 288 | $33.17 | 5.2% |\n    37→| Write | 138 | $25.36 | 3.9% |\n    38→| TodoWrite | 105 | $14.40 | 2.2% |\n    39→| Glob | 84 | $13.06 | 2.0% |\n    40→| ToolSearch | 26 | $2.90 | 0.5% |\n    41→\n    42→## Top 10 Most Expensive Stories\n    43→\n    44→| Story | Calls | Cost | % |\n    45→|-------|-------|------|---|\n    46→| unknown | 624 | $129.83 | 20.2% |\n    47→| 14-5-stack-aware-verify-dockerfile | 190 | $23.63 | 3.7% |\n    48→| 14-4-observability-backend-choice | 192 | $22.13 | 3.4% |\n    49→| 8-9-semgrep-rules-rust-observability | 121 | $17.10 | 2.7% |\n    50→| 8-2-expand-state-types-for-rust | 84 | $12.67 | 2.0% |\n    51→| 9-5-multi-stack-docs-remaining-consumers | 84 | $11.07 | 1.7% |\n    52→| 16-5-rewrite-harness-run-verification-dispatch | 104 | $10.85 | 1.7% |\n    53→| 11-2-sprint-status-yaml-derived-view | 74 | $10.80 | 1.7% |\n    54→| 11-1-unified-sprintstate-schema-versioning | 75 | $10.27 | 1.6% |\n    55→| 12-4-shared-test-utilities-fixtures | 85 | $9.98 | 1.6% |"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_01FuRY7MubihCm9AuNVcYqKC","session_id":"94a00213-6144-4c24-a440-4acde8467da0","uuid":"39b75572-de04-42ac-acb6-cce05deb3eb3","timestamp":"2026-03-27T14:52:08.152Z"}
